parent1.code: A watercolor of three vibrant hummingbirds in the style of magical realism. They hover around a giant, bioluminescent flower in a misty rainforest at twilight, sipping nectar from its petals, with glowing fireflies and mysterious floating orbs illuminating the scene.

parent2.code: A mesmerizing watercolor of three iridescent hummingbirds in the style of surrealist magical realism. They gracefully hover around a colossal bioluminescent flower in a mystical rainforest at twilight, delicately sipping shimmering nectar from its translucent petals, with enchanted fireflies and prismatic orbs illuminating the dreamlike scene.

offspring.code: A whimsical sketch of five ethereal jellyfish in the style of steampunk fantasy. They float gracefully through a submerged clockwork city in the depths of an alien ocean, their tentacles intertwining with gears and springs, as bioluminescent plankton swirl around them, illuminating the rusty mechanical structures and forgotten treasures scattered across the seafloor.
